      "title": "How To Qualify For A Free 5G Phone?",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Qualify For A Free 5G Phone?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. What Programs Can Connect You To 5G?</h4>\n<p>The government offers free 5G phones mainly through two programs: Lifeline and Affordable Connectivity. These programs help make sure everyone can use 5G technology, even if they have limited money. They provide fast internet and better phone features.</p>\n<img alt=\"How To Qualify For A Free 5G Phone?_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
