      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Qualify For A Free 5G Phone?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>2. Meeting Criteria For 5G Phones</h4>\n<p>To get a free 5G government phone, you need to meet certain rules. Your eligibility depends on how much you earn or if you are part of federal help programs like SNAP, Medicaid, or FPHA. For Lifeline, your income should be 135% or less of the federal poverty level, and for ACP, it should be 200% or less. Being in some government programs also makes you eligible.</p>\n<img alt=\"How To Qualify For A Free 5G Phone?_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone/how-to-qualify-for-a-free-5g-phone_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
